profile: Georgina Cut'n Clean Property Services strive to serve our customers with the most affordable, reliable and honest property care. In doing so we offer multiple lawn maintenance, Snow removal and other property maintenance packages for our customers to choose from.  We are a husband and wife that decided we wanted to help keep their community a beautiful and clean place to live for all that live here. Georgina Cut’n Clean Property Services is a family owned and operated local business with over 10 years of experience that specializes in residential lawn maintenance and Snow removal.

profile:
NATURAL TURF
Natural Turf has been providing innovative organic lawn care services for over ten years.

The company is renowned for creating exclusively customized turf care programs for you, the homeowner that suits the unique growing conditions in your location.  At the foundation of its lawn care services is the principle of feeding the soil first and then in turn feeding the turf.  This creates a well-balanced growing environment for your lawn.

Natural Turf will come to your home and provide you with a complementary lawn analysis that will be the foundation of a customized turf care program tailor-made for your lawn.  Every Natural Turf lawn care program is organic-based.
